longBusinessSummary: Dacian Gold Limited engages in the exploration, mining, and processing of gold properties in Australia. The company holds interest in Mt Morgans and the Redcliffe gold project located in Leonora-Laverton, Western Australia. Dacian Gold Limited was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Perth, Australia. Dacian Gold Limited operates as a subsidiary of Genesis Minerals Limited.
